; [14] USB surprise removal / AttemptRecovery
[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\USB\AutomaticSurpriseRemovals]
"AttemptRecoveryFromUsbPowerDrain"=dword:00000000
